  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Extraordinary regulatory framework: VTQ, Covid-19 Conditions and Requirements
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This document sets out our regulatory requirements for awarding organisations offering vocational and technical qualifications during the Coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic.</p>

  </div>
</div>

