      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="requirements-set-out-in-this-document">Requirements set out in this document</h2>

<p>This document sets out the Extended VTQ coronavirus (COVID-19) Conditions. These conditions come into effect at 15:00 on 12 October 2020 for all vocational and technical qualifications as defined in Condition ExtVTQCov1.8.</p>

<p>It also sets out our requirements in relation to the following:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the Adaptation of vocational and technical qualifications.</li>
  <li>the principles to be applied by awarding organisations when Adapting vocational and technical qualifications.</li>
</ul>

<p>With respect to all vocational and technical qualifications to which the conditions set out in this document apply, save to the extent set out in those conditions, awarding organisations must also comply with:</p>

<ul>
  <li>our General Conditions of Recognition, which apply to all awarding organisations and qualifications, and</li>
  <li>all relevant Regulatory Documents</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

      </section>
